sequenceDiagram
    participant Harness as Unified profiler harness
    participant Auto as auto-infer
    participant Omni as omni-npu
    participant Ascend as vllm-ascend

    Harness->>Auto: PREFILL
    activate Auto
    Auto-->>Harness: first token
    deactivate Auto
    loop DECODE 001 to 015
        Harness->>Auto: engine step
        Auto-->>Harness: next token
    end

    Harness->>Omni: PREFILL
    activate Omni
    Omni-->>Harness: async scheduled output
    deactivate Omni
    loop DECODE 001 to 015
        Harness->>Omni: engine step
        Omni-->>Harness: next token
    end
    Harness->>Omni: RUNTIME DRAIN
    Omni-->>Harness: flush terminal async output

    Harness->>Ascend: PREFILL
    activate Ascend
    Ascend-->>Harness: async scheduled output
    deactivate Ascend
    loop DECODE 001 to 015
        Harness->>Ascend: engine step
        Ascend-->>Harness: next token
    end
    Harness->>Ascend: RUNTIME DRAIN
    Ascend-->>Harness: flush terminal async output

    Note over Harness,Ascend: QWEN3 PHASES lane contains only 1 PREFILL and 15 DECODE ranges, while runtime drains stay visible outside decode.
